export const UserContext = createContext()

function App() {
  const [list, setList] = useLocalStorage('list', exercises)

  useEffect (() => {
    document.body.style.backgroundColor = '#efebe9';
  })
  
  return (
  <>
  <UserContext.Provider value={{list, setList}}>
  <CssBaseline />
    <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
      <Router>
        <Routes>
          <Route path='/' element={<Home/>} />
          <Route path='/CreateRoutine' element={<CreateRoutine/>} />
          <Route path='/Phase1Create' element={<Phase1Create/>} />
          <Route path='/DragExercises' element={<DragExercises/>} />
          <Route path='*' element={<Error404/>} />
        </Routes>

    </ThemeProvider>

}


export default App;
